node_6.description: This is Klaus Mueller's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am, have breakfast at 7:45 am, go to the library at Oak Hill College at 8:30 am, write a research paper at 9:00 am, take a short break and have a snack at 11:00 am, finish writing the research paper by 1:00 pm, go to Hobbs Cafe for lunch at 12:00 pm, spend time exploring other perspectives in the library at 1:45 pm.
